text: == Events == * March 26 – Pope John XIX crowns Conrad II, Holy Roman Emperor. * May 14 – Henry I of France is crowned king of France at Reims Cathedral. * Aldred becomes abbot of Tavistock. * Start of the Tibetan calendar. == Births == * October 14 - William the Conqueror, King of England and Duke of Normandy (died 1087) == Deaths == * Richard, Duke of Normandy, French nobleman (born 960) == References ==
